This paper deals with facial recognition using deep learning algorithms, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also mentions the use of support vector machines (SVM) for classification, which is a popular machine learning technique and falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions real-time performance, which suggests that it may fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) category. Finally, the paper deals with security and intrusion detection, which may also suggest the computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) category.
